<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Hidden Level -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>You must destroy the C-5 transport on the first raven level in order to unlock the hidden mission level.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock the XFA-27 Fighter -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Beat the game on normal. Play the game again on hard and make your way to the ''Dead-End'' mission. Destroy the four YF-23A's in the special Fox Force Four squadron south of the target to unlock the XFA-27 and a medal at the Debriefing screen.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; View 3D Aircrafts -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Shoot down all Skilled enemy pilots and collect all the medals in the Statistics screen. A new option appears in the Options menu that lets you view all the planes you've encountered.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Bad Ending -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Beat the pilot Z.O.E in mission 19 to access mission 20. In mission 20, do not shoot down the cruise missile, and you'll unlock the bad ending of the game</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Bonus Ending -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>In mission 20, shoot down the cruise missile to advance to the bonus mission: Fighter's Honor. Defeat that mission to unlock the Bonus Mission.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Music Test -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>To access the Music Player, beat the game with a rank above First Lieutenant. Then access the options menu to play all of the game's music.</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Normal Ending -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>Make your way to the 19th mission ''Kingpin'', and beat the mission without destroying the skilled enemy pilot Z.O.E</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite energy -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8002CEEC 0000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Money -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80010C1C 967F<br>80010C1E 0098</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Infinite Fuel All - Break Point Code -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80039E1C 0000<br>80039E1E 0000</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock all Hidden Aircrafts -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80010C44 0101<br>80010C46 0101<br>80010C48 0101<br>80010C4A 0101<br>80010C4C 0101<br>80010C4E 0101<br>80010C50 0101<br>80010C52 0101</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>

     </tr>
</table>

